<span id="freeTextContainer10947961082054461048">This a wonderful book full of rich characters, a puzzling mystery that will have you engrossed in no time. Elizabeth Hunter has built a paranormal world that has characters with their own unique abilities. But there’s no bigger mystery than our own hero Giovanni. There’s definitely more to this character that meets the eye and he’s absolutely gorgeous!<br/><br/>Beatrice our heroine is bubbly, intelligent and is a perfect match for Gio. The romance is fabulously written. It&apos;s not a quick romp when they fir</span>
  <span id="freeText10947961082054461048" style="display:none">This a wonderful book full of rich characters, a puzzling mystery that will have you engrossed in no time. Elizabeth Hunter has built a paranormal world that has characters with their own unique abilities. But there’s no bigger mystery than our own hero Giovanni. There’s definitely more to this character that meets the eye and he’s absolutely gorgeous!<br /><br />Beatrice our heroine is bubbly, intelligent and is a perfect match for Gio. The romance is fabulously written. It's not a quick romp when they first meet. It starts out small and it slowly builds. The sexual tension is constanly simmering in the background and the heat gets a little hotter with each encounter. Love it! <br /><br />For all you PNR lovers out there, this is a real treat so give it a go!<br /></span>
