<li class='cover' id='bookCover_57109937'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/57109937-magical-midlife-meeting"><img alt="Magical Midlife Meeting (Leveling Up #5)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1613591321l/57109937._SX98_.jpg" />
