  <span id="freeText10605834942325286519" style="display:none">ELIZABETH HUNTER is a USA Today and international bestselling author of romance, contemporary fantasy, and paranormal mystery. Based in Central California, she travels extensively to write fantasy fiction exploring world mythologies, history, and the universal bonds of love, friendship, and family. <br /><br />She has published over thirty works of fiction and sold over a million books world-wide. She is the author of Love Stories on 7th and Main, the Elemental Legacy series, the Irin Chronicles, the Cambio Springs Mysteries, and other works of fiction.<br /><br />Sign up for her newsletter to receive exclusive bonus content, advance previews, and alerts about new releases and sales.<br /><br />New releases: <br />Elemental Legacy series—Midnight Labyrinth (now available)<br />7th and Main—INK (March 13, available for preorder)<br />Irin Chronicles—The Storm (April 17, available for preorder) </span>
